# direnv -> nix flake bridge
# Activates the devShell defined in flake.nix when entering this directory.
#
# Requirements: direnv (installed) + nix-direnv. Until Nix is installed this
# file is a no-op; once Nix lands, run `direnv allow` to enable.
#
# Falls back to `use flake` (built-in) if nix-direnv isn't present.
if has nix_direnv_version; then
  use flake
elif has nix && [ -f flake.nix ]; then
  use flake
fi
